data.description: $5000 concession, Well maintained home, conveniently located walking distance from Midlothian Heritage High school, and many other places such as HEB, downtown Waxahachie just a 15 min drive. The home offers an open floor plan, a kitchen with eat in bar and granite countertops, bedrooms have new carpet installed. Master bedroom offers dual sink vanity, shower and jetted walk in tub, nice size back yard and two car garage, come make this your new home as a new proud Midlothian resident!
